title: Supercars.Exposed-Speed2008-Hawaii.Exotics-Mekhi.Ferrari
description: SuperCars Exposed, Speed Channel (US) 2008, Hosted by Tanner Foust, 22 mins.  Tanner joins a supercar tour of Hawaii arranged by World Class Driving.  Actor Mekhi Phifer goes shopping for a super car.  Cars featured: McLaren Mercedes SLR, Lamborghinis (including a Gallardo Superleggera), Ferrari 599 GTB, Porsches, Ford GT, Chevy Corvette C6 Z06.  MP4 file, H264 codec, 640x480, captured from digital SDTV.  More episodes to come from tallearthling.
